<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Soft Girl Aesthetic</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #ffe6f0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #555;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #ff99cc;
        }
        .card {
            background-color: #fff0f5;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 60%;
            margin: auto;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="card">
        <h1>Soft Girl 🌸</h1>
        <p>
            A soft girl is someone who embraces a gentle, cute, and pastel aesthetic.
            This style often includes light colors like pink and lavender, cozy outfits,
            and a love for simple, happy things.
        </p>
        <p>
            The soft girl vibe focuses on kindness, positivity, and a calm, dreamy look.
            It is often expressed through fashion, makeup, and lifestyle choices.
        </p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>